SIMPLE: hotshot
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hotshot
<hw>Hot"shot`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a successful, self-confident
person who is regarded by others as highly skilled; -- sometimes used
ironically in reference to aggressive persons whose opinion of their own
talents is considered exaggerated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>hotshot</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: hotshot
<hw>hot"shot`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>highly talented,
self-confident and successful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>flamboyantly displaying one's skills.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hot-spirited</ent>⟦br⟧
